com.orange.api.rfid.capture.application.server.configure
Class ConfigureManager

java.lang.Object
  com.orange.api.rfid.capture.application.server.configure.ConfigureManager

public class ConfigureManager
extends java.lang.Object

This class is called by ConfigureImpl web methods to manage reading, writing and deleting of single:

  • BusinessProcessEvent
  • CaptureEvent
  • QueryEvent
  • GPIOEvent
  • SubscriberEvent
  • VocabularyObject
  • BusinessProcessObject
It also manages post, get and delete actions for VocabularyElementType and BPEventElementType.

Author:
Benoit Plomion, Marc-Antoine Mouilleron Orange

get

public static GetResult get(Poll parms)
                     throws java.lang.Exception
Gets entries according to Poll parameters. Parameters should include:
  • class: either Vocabulary or BPEvent. Omitting this parameter returns both.
  • type in URN format, if class is Vocabulary. E.g. urn:epcglobal:epcis:vtype:BusinessLocation
  • id, with type mandatory for Vocabulary entries. E.g. urn:epc:id:sgln:318757.00010.6921000

Parameters:
parms - Poll parameters
Returns:
result GetResult XML document
Throws:
java.lang.Exception
